sub_title: Food technologist with a specialisation in Product design
summary:
“I am equipped with science and technology applied to food and specialised in food product design. I aspire to harness every potential in me to better the lots of humanity by contributing significantly to the goals of companies and institutions which by researches, innovations and creativities seek to improve the needs of humanity. I value feedback and learn fast from my mistakes. I value innovation and creativity. I want to do more to make an impact, improve processes & products, enhance quality, safety and develop sustainable products by working with innovative people in building a result-oriented multidisciplinary team.”


Innovative - Creative - Committed - Teachable
